{"tid":680546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 餐廳前僱員持刀追薪　涉恐嚇女店東被捕","createTime":"2018-05-27T09:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T09:40:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb82b52bfb15ea2f53300a989134e5604da9418","tid":680546,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"荃灣昨晚有男子出刀追薪被捕。昨晚9時許，姓羅(31歲)男子，持刀到永順街一餐廳，與姓羅(44歲)女店東理論，期間羅報稱遭人出言恐嚇，於是報警求助。警員到場初步調查後，以涉嫌刑事恐嚇將羅拘捕，案件交荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進。據悉，羂為該餐廳前僱員，疑返上址追薪。有街坊指，事前曾見一名可疑男子在附近荃灣海濱公園平台出現，嚇得街坊大驚，懷疑他便是案中疑犯，當時正前往餐廳途中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/bkn-20180527143124759-0527_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180527%2Fbkn-20180527143124759-0527_00822_001.html&d=GXNzoZh0xSHPFw8hkR3%2Bf04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=9cec25c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180527/bkn-20180527143124759-0527_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6606ebba5248dd99844d8d9b4a3ac5de6ca06137","tid":680546,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"返工=No paid"},{"pid":"95aa46d9bc594733cf3c78a4471aa8e10629966f","tid":680546,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}